Description:
Fantastic family home in Newcomb.
A fantastic family home in Newcomb with open plan living, great natural light, and a huge undercover alfresco entertaining area. This 4 bedroom, 3 living, plus study and 2 bathroom home is set on 848m2 of land (approx).
Upon entry there is a separate lounge room, the master bedroom has WIRs & ensuite to the left, the onto a study/home office. The home has 3 other generous sized bedrooms all with BIRs and a second central bathroom. The main living area is comprised of kitchen/dining area, that overlooks the second lounge and a
rumpus room to the rear of the home. Step outside to the undercover entertaining area where the whole family and friends can enjoy endless BBQs and great times together. The large backyard has plenty of room for the kids and includes a garden shed. The double garage has drive through access to the back yard.
Features of this property include, large block, ducted heating, gas cooktop, dishwasher, multiple living zones, fantastic north facing living, Court location, all this within a few minutes from the Geelong CBD & waterfront, schools and shopping centres. Don't miss your opportunity to secure a fantastic family home, in the ever popular suburb of Newcomb.

This newly updated 4 bed, 2 bath, 2 living brick property set on 706m2 will suit an array of buyers. Freshly painted and carpeted throughout this wonderful property would appeal to a growing family with great size back yard and open plan living, a downsizer looking for trailer, caravan side access or a Savvy investor with a potential rent $430 pw.
Comprising of a bright formal living room located at the front of the property ideal for reading or watching a movie. Following the brand new flooring down the hall you will find a huge open plan living/dining/kitchen area. The perfect space for the whole family to unwind.
The kitchen offers brand new splash back tiling, SS appliances, a handy dishwasher plus a long breakfast bar which easily seats up to 6.
The dining area flows nicely off the kitchen and has sliding doors leading to the paved outside entertaining area.
The Master bedroom is spacious and offers brand new carpet, block-out blinds and WIR plus the newly renovated ensuite is fitted with Italian luxe feel tiles, Caesar stone finishes and offers rain shower head and tastic heat-lamps.
Located towards the rear of the home you will find an additional 3 more bedrooms all with BIR and a fully renovated luxe central bathroom with modern full size freestanding bath, quality tap-wear and Caesar stone vanity and rain shower head for all your family needs.
Outside there is a great size rear yard, landscaped gardens and shedding facilities. The double side gates allows for handy trailer, campervan or bike access. This great property is ideally located in growing St Albans Park less than 4km from Geelong CBD, walking distance to local parks and 2km to Newcomb Shopping Centre.
FEATURES
706m2 Block
Rent pw $430 approx
Ducted Heating
Rev cycle Split system
Side access
New flooring

Description:
Clinker Brick Loaded with Potential
This charming clinker brick home offers buyer's original retro features and endless options for renovation or extension (STCA), all in a quiet street within a popular pocket of East Geelong.
Comprising of 2 bedrooms, main bedroom is spacious in size and fitted with floor to ceiling BIR's, while bedroom two also has BIR's.
A large family / living area is brightly lit by natural light coming through the large windows and includes a new gas heater. The dining space is located adjacent, which leads through to the kitchen, fitted with electric appliances and loads of storage space. To finish inside, a neat central bathroom and a separate laundry.
Outside, the 557sqm block (approx) leaves you with great sized back yard and also has a single garage, storage shed which could be used as a bungalow with some TLC and low maintenance gardens.
The home is located only minutes' drive from South Geelong train station, Geelong High School, Garden Street shops and the C.B.D. Put your own stamp on the property or leave as is. The home provides the rarest of opportunities and will appeal to any genuine buyer searching for value in a growth suburb.

Description:
DELIGHTFUL LIFESTYLE PROPERTY CLOSE TO TOWN
9 Acres “LINOLA” 3.8 Hectares (approx.)
SUPERBLY LOCATED 20 MINUTES GEELONG - 10 MINUTES RING ROAD
BRILLIANT ACCESS TO SURF COAST BEACHES
This superbly located country property offers convenient rural living, room for a pony or livestock providing relaxing country views over farmland and the You Yangs.
• 3 bedrooms (main ensuite & WI robe) office (or 4th bedroom). Formal lounge with feature open fireplace and generously proportioned rumpus room. Main bathroom (spa) laundry, separate toilet.
• Spacious country kitchen with wall oven and bench top hotplates, meals area, walk-in pantry plus storage room. Other features include slab heating, evaporative cooling and 2 car under roofline garage. Domestic water via 20,000 gallons tank supplies plus dam.
• Modern steel machinery / farm shed 12m x 7.5m (lock up) with roller doors.
• School bus access to Geelong schools with daily mail and fortnightly rubbish.

Address: 8 Ottoman Court St Albans Park VIC 3219
Description:
Great Opportunity in Quiet Court Location.
This is home is located in a lovely quiet court recently refurbished with new floor coverings, blinds, freshly painted, lockable single car garage and all on a large block of 569m2 (approx.) Ready to move straight in. Comprising original, spacious open plan kitchen, very neat bathroom with shower & bath, 3 spacious bedrooms and main living area with big window, double blinds with lovely sun streaming in from the northerly aspect. Also offering aluminium windows, split system, gas wall furnace, pergola, long drive for off street parking.
Located just 10 minutes from the CBD, close to a local park, with having easy access to public transport, this home is a great opportunity to add to your investment portfolio.
Rental estimate between $310-320 pw.
